<dl id="n11026f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11026f">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11026f"> 26(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> slow fire</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>La Pers&eacute;cution</b> Chaque province a son supplice particulier: le feu lent en M&eacute;sopotamie, la roue dans le Pont, la hache en Arabie, le plomb fondu en Capadoce. <br><font color="green">[Every province has its own torture: <mark>slow fire</mark> in Mesopotamia, the wheel in Pontus, the axe in Arabia, molten lead in Cappadocia.]</font> <small> Chateaubriand, <a name="CHBD" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CHBD"><cite title="source">&OElig;uvres choisies illustr&eacute;es</cite></a> (1912) II, <i>Les Martyrs</i> 85</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
